{{short description|State where a planet's atmosphere rotates faster than the planet itself}} 
'''大气层超自转''' (Atmospheric super-rotation) 是指一颗[[行星|行星]]的[[大气层|大气层]]比行星本身旋转更快的状态。[[金星大气层|金星大气层]]就是一个极端超自转的示例，它的大气层仅用4个地球日就绕行星一周，比金星243[[日|天]]的[[恒星日|恒星日]]要快得多 <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sci.esa.int/web/venus-express/-/54065-4-super-rotation-is-speeding-up|title=ESA Science & Technology - Major Discoveries by Venus Express: 2006-2014|website=sci.esa.int|access-date=2020-01-21|archive-date=2020-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200420185739/https://sci.esa.int/web/venus-express/-/54065-4-super-rotation-is-speeding-up|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[土星|土星]]最大的卫星[[土卫六|土卫六]]上也观测到大气层超旋转的现象<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Read|first=Peter L.|last2=Lebonnois|first2=Sebastien|date=2018|title=Superrotation on Venus, on Titan, and Elsewhere|journal=Annual Review of Earth and Planetary Sciences|volume=46|issue=1|pages=175–202|doi=10.1146/annurev-earth-082517-010137}}</ref>。

据信，地球的[[热层|热层]]有一比地表旋转速度更快的小型超旋转网，尽管对该现象的估值相差很大<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Gaposchkin|first=E. M|date=2003-05-01|title=Atmospheric superrotation?|journal=Planetary and Space Science|language=en|volume=51|issue=6|pages=415–425|doi=10.1016/S0032-0633(03)00021-7|issn=0032-0633}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last=Blum|first=P. W.|last2=Harris|first2=I.|date=1974-06-01|title=Some new aspects on the superrotation of the thermosphere|journal=Journal of Atmospheric and Terrestrial Physics|language=en|volume=36|issue=6|pages=967–978|doi=10.1016/0021-9169(74)90006-3|issn=0021-9169|hdl=2060/19730011711|hdl-access=free}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last=Rishbeth|first=H.|date=January 1971|title=Rotation of the Variation of Upper Atmosphere|journal=Nature|language=en|volume=229|issue=5283|pages=333–334|doi=10.1038/229333a0|pmid=16059224|issn=1476-4687}}</ref> ，部分模型预测表明，[[全球变暖|全球变暖]]可能会导致未来超自转现象的增强，包括可能形成的超级旋风<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Carlson|first=Henrik|last2=Caballero|first2=Rodrigo|date=March 2016|title=Enhanced MJO and transition to superrotation in warm climates|journal=Journal of Advances in Modeling Earth Systems|volume=8|issue=1|pages=304–318|doi=10.1002/2015ms000615|issn=1942-2466|doi-access=free}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|last=Caballero|first=Rodrigo|last2=Carlson|first2=Henrik|date=October 2018|title=Surface Superrotation|journal=Journal of the Atmospheric Sciences|language=en|volume=75|issue=10|pages=3671–3689|doi=10.1175/JAS-D-18-0076.1|issn=0022-4928|doi-access=free}}</ref>。

